headline.main: TOBRUK DEFENDERS REPEL TANK ATTACK; Axis Forces Goaded to Strike by Prodding of Australian and Polish Patrols

lead_paragraph: CAIRO, Egypt, Nov. 13 -- After weeks of nightly goading by Australian and Polish patrols from Tobruk, Axis forces again launched a drive with tanks last night in an attempt to regain control of the No Man's Land.
